Titolo: Half-Life: C.A.G.E.D.

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Half-Life: C.A.G.E.D. (also stylized as Half-Life: Caged)  is a game modification of Half-Life by Cayle George and Future Games Select released on September 21, 2017. Made using the GoldSrc engine, the mod includes a single-player campaign in which the player must escape from a closely guarded prison.The mod was released on Microsoft Windows via Steam and was made available on OS X and Linux in December 2017.